util

Interface IDispatcher<TDispMsg>

  • Type Parameters:
    TDispMsg - The type of messages being dispatched
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ACollectionDispatcher, ASetDispatcher, SetDispatcherSequential

    public interface IDispatcher<TDispMsg>
    An dispatcher of messages of type TDispMsg to its registered IObserver objects. The dispatcher is an Observable in the Observer-Observable design pattern though with the difference of always immediately dispatching to the observers when a message is received.
    Author:
    Suozhi Qi, Zhaohan Jia
